3 、4 、8 所示之物均沒收。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCHM/110%2c%e5%8e%9f%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c19%2c20211019%2c3/pdf"},"JID":"TCHM,110,原上訴,19,20211019,3","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"原上訴","JNO":"19","JDATE":"20211019","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}